@startuml
title Secuencia - Diagnostico IA desde Aplicacion Movil

actor "Responsable de Area" as Responsable
boundary "App Movil React Native" as Mobile
control "Camara Nativa" as Camera
control "MS2 IAController" as IAController
control "DiagnosticoIAService" as DiagnosticoService
control "ModelLoader" as ModelLoader
control "CNN Estado Activo" as CNN
control "S3Adapter" as S3Adapter
control "DynamoDBAdapter" as DynamoAdapter
database "Amazon S3" as S3
database "DynamoDB" as DynamoDB
control "MS3 Webhook" as MS3

Responsable -> Mobile : Selecciona activo y solicita fotografia
Mobile -> Camera : solicitarPermisoCamara()
Camera --> Mobile : permiso concedido
Mobile -> Camera : capturarImagen()
Camera --> Mobile : imagenUri
Mobile -> IAController : POST /api/ia/diagnostico(FormData)
IAController -> DiagnosticoService : inferir(imagen, activoId)
DiagnosticoService -> DiagnosticoService : validar calidad y presencia visual
DiagnosticoService -> ModelLoader : cargar CNN si disponible
ModelLoader --> DiagnosticoService : modelo
DiagnosticoService -> CNN : predecir(imagen 224x224)
CNN --> DiagnosticoService : senal auxiliar
DiagnosticoService -> S3Adapter : almacenar imagen
S3Adapter -> S3 : PUT verificaciones/{activoId}/{uuid}.jpg
S3 --> S3Adapter : s3Key
DiagnosticoService -> DynamoAdapter : guardar diagnostico auditable
DynamoAdapter -> DynamoDB : PUT diagnostico
DiagnosticoService --> IAController : resultado, confianza, detalle
IAController -> MS3 : POST diagnostico critico si aplica
MS3 --> IAController : 202 Accepted
IAController --> Mobile : JSON diagnostico
Mobile --> Responsable : Muestra resultado y recomendaciones

@enduml

